  "page": {
    "documentTitle": "現狀偏誤 | Concept Reading Lab",
    "bodyClass": "knowledge-page knowledge-status-quo-bias",
    "heroHtml": "<div class=\"hero-inner\">\n  <div>\n    <p class=\"kicker\">Knowledge Study / defaults / decision / change</p>\n    <h1>現狀偏誤</h1>\n    <p class=\"topic-subtitle\">Status Quo Bias</p>\n    <p class=\"thesis\">維持現狀常被感覺成中立，但很多時候它其實也是一種有代價的選擇，只是風險被藏在不作為裡。</p>\n    <div class=\"hero-prompt\">\n      <strong>Read For</strong>\n      <p>這一頁要把『先不要動』的安心感和『其實已在為現狀付費』拆開，因為很多保守決策真正躲的是被看不見的代價。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <aside class=\"hero-note\" aria-label=\"主題資訊\">\n    <dl class=\"lexical-meta lexical-meta--knowledge\" aria-label=\"主題摘要\">\n      <div>\n        <dt>主題類型</dt>\n        <dd>決策偏誤 / 預設依附</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>核心問題</dt>\n        <dd>People disproportionately prefer the current state</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>主要判準</dt>\n        <dd>預設力量、切換成本、損失感、替代方案清晰度</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>讀完產出</dt>\n        <dd>能分辨哪些決策是在理性保守，哪些只是被預設與慣性推著留在原地</dd>\n      </div>\n    </dl>\n    <div class=\"knowledge-map\" aria-label=\"閱讀結構示意\">\n      <span>預設</span>\n      <span>慣性</span>\n      <span>代價</span>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n</div>",
    "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"compass\" aria-label=\"頁內導覽\">\n  <span>Reading Path</span>\n  <a href=\"#core\">讀法總覽</a>\n  <a href=\"#setup\">問題設定</a>\n  <a href=\"#lenses\">判準透鏡</a>\n  <a href=\"#psychology\">心理連結</a>\n  <a href=\"#applications\">現實映射</a>\n  <a href=\"#misreadings\">誤讀校正</a>\n  <a href=\"#questions\">延伸提問</a>\n  <a href=\"#sources\">來源</a>\n</aside>\n\n<article class=\"article\">\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"core\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Orientation</p>\n      <h2>不改，不代表沒有選；很多時候只是把選擇包裝成自然延續</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">現狀偏誤提醒你：人對現有配置的偏好，常超過它實際值得的程度。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"core-card\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Core Tension</p>\n      <p>保留現狀能降低短期不確定，但也會讓過時設計、低效流程與錯失機會持續累積成本。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"principle-strip\" aria-label=\"本頁讀法\">\n      <div>\n        <span>01</span>\n        <strong>先把現狀也當成選項</strong>\n        <p>只要看見維持原狀同樣有成本，判斷就會比較公平。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>02</span>\n        <strong>再拆開真風險與熟悉感</strong>\n        <p>很多『先不要』其實不是風險分析，而是對不熟的抗拒。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>03</span>\n        <strong>最後降低切換摩擦</strong>\n        <p>若替代方案很難試、很難退，現狀偏誤就會被制度放大。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"setup\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Setup</p>\n      <h2>從一個大家都知道不理想、卻一直沒換掉的流程開始</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">現狀偏誤常不會以戲劇方式出現，而是以一連串『先這樣就好』慢慢定居。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>最小劇情</strong>\n        <p>團隊都知道現有 issue 流程很繞，但因為搬遷成本、學習成本與短期不確定，最後大家還是繼續用。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>真正難點</strong>\n        <p>真正被高估的常不是新方案風險，而是現狀的無形安全感。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"concept-flow\" aria-label=\"問題展開\">\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">現狀成為預設</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">替代方案看起來有切換痛</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">維持原狀被誤當成中立</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"paradox-frame\">\n      <strong>Key Point</strong>\n      <p>現狀偏誤最值得警覺的地方，是它會把時間推移本身造成的代價藏起來。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"lenses\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Lenses</p>\n      <h2>四個看預設慣性的角度</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">不是所有維持現狀都錯，但你至少要知道自己在守什麼。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"lens-grid\">\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>熟悉紅利</strong>\n        <p>現狀是不是因為熟悉，而不是因為真的更好？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>切換摩擦</strong>\n        <p>新方案是否因導入過程麻煩而被過度懲罰？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>隱性成本</strong>\n        <p>現狀正在持續吞掉哪些時間、品質或機會？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>可逆程度</strong>\n        <p>如果新方案可試可退，現狀偏誤通常就比較容易被鬆動。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>情境</th>\n            <th>現狀偏誤看起來像</th>\n            <th>被遮住的成本</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>工具更換</td>\n            <td>大家都習慣了別動</td>\n            <td>效率損失與知識摩擦持續累積</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>產品預設</td>\n            <td>先維持目前流程</td>\n            <td>使用者一直在繞路但數據未必立即顯示</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>職涯選擇</td>\n            <td>現在至少安全</td>\n            <td>長期磨耗與成長停滯被視為背景雜訊</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"psychology\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Psychology</p>\n      <h2>為什麼現狀看起來總比較沒風險</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">因為現狀的代價多半分散在時間裡，不像改變那樣在前面就顯得刺眼。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>熟悉感被誤讀成安全</strong>\n        <p>人很容易把已知的不舒服看得比未知的可能性更可承受。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>切換痛會被放大</strong>\n        <p>導入與學習成本通常在短期非常可見。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>不作為像是沒有責任</strong>\n        <p>選擇不改時，失敗常被解讀成自然延續而不是決策結果。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"micro-note\">現狀偏誤不是反保守，而是反對把熟悉誤認成中立。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"applications\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Applications</p>\n      <h2>把預設意識帶回流程與產品設計</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">對工程與產品團隊來說，很多該改的東西之所以沒改，不是因為評估後不值得，而是因為現狀自己會說話。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>流程改革</strong>\n        <p>若沒有低風險試點，大家自然會高估改變成本、低估原流程成本。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>產品預設設定</strong>\n        <p>使用者常沿用預設，不代表預設真最適合，只代表切換本身有摩擦。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>技術債治理</strong>\n        <p>架構拖著不動時，現狀偏誤會把『先別動』包裝成穩健。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\n      <li>做選項比較時，把『維持現狀』也寫成顯性方案，連同代價一起估。</li>\n      <li>若想對抗現狀偏誤，先把替代方案做成可逆、可試、低承諾的版本。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"misreadings\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Misreadings</p>\n      <h2>三個常見誤讀</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">現狀偏誤不是說所有不變都錯，而是提醒你很多不變其實不是中立。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"collocation-list\" aria-label=\"常見誤讀\">\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>只要願意改就是進步</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>不是。重點是不要讓預設本身偷走判斷。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>保守就是偏誤</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>保守可以理性，但要建立在看見現狀成本之後。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>這只發生在個人選擇</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>制度、產品預設與團隊流程都會放大它。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"questions\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Questions</p>\n      <h2>我是在保護價值，還是在被預設牽著走</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">下面兩個問題很適合放在變更評估前。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prompt-grid\">\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>如果今天從零開始，我還會選現在這個預設嗎</strong>\n        <p>若不會，現狀偏誤就很可能已在工作。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>不改的成本是否也被我像改的成本那樣認真看待</strong>\n        <p>若沒有，評估本身就已經歪了。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"template-note\">\n      <strong>延伸路線</strong>\n      <p>延伸閱讀可接 default effect、loss aversion 與 switching cost。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"sources\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Sources</p>\n      <h2>來源與整理方式</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">這一頁以 status quo bias 為主，再把概念帶回產品預設、流程改革與個人決策。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"source-grid\">\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>主概念</strong>\n        <p>Status quo bias 條目整理了人如何傾向偏好現有狀態。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Status_quo_bias\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Status Quo Bias</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>近鄰概念</strong>\n        <p>Default effect 可作為對照，看預設值如何系統性影響選擇。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Default_effect\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Default Effect</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>相鄰偏誤</strong>\n        <p>Loss aversion 有助於理解為何改變看起來總特別像風險。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loss_aversion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Loss Aversion</a>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\">\n    <div class=\"reference-box\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"section-label\">Reference</p>\n        <h2>下一步</h2>\n        <p>讀完後可以挑一個你一直說之後再改的流程，把『維持現狀的成本』寫成一張清單。</p>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"reference-link\" href=\"../knowledge-topic-template.html\">打開模板</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</article>"
  }
}
